Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是母親的資料文件而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是最新世代的NEO-GIN的母體遺傳基因提供者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是瑪麗亞的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 兌現了承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們來檢查一下現在裝備了CloneBlade的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你很期待哦 瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是最完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不能在一起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩潰在繼續著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也確認了精神狀態產生混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有預想中的深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許和之前崩潰的志織一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說這就是這次想要確認的所謂母親的感情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是咖啡奶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好安靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是我父親建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是在安慰我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不說的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算聯絡上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之　你馬上去接梨穗子回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NswF的那些姐妹不單只是由被選擇的遺傳基因出生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們自己也被作為母體提供遺傳基因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是聞所未聞的近親交配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近親? 什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 所有姐妹的父親的遺傳基因都是一個人提供的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進而 下個世代的姐妹們也是用相同的父親的遺傳基因 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於那個男人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些姐妹即是女兒也是妻子 還是孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我猜測 那個父親就是教父 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這麼做我是不知道 但一定不是些什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管離NswF有多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穌峰玲奈也是姐妹中的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那傢伙不是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把梨穗子帶回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她和那種怪物在一起的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正·胸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:05:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有要回來的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼資格啊 明明那麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說Lady是怪物 要我把梨穗子接回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有資格這麼說人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady救過梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有錢 又是醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說 她是真正的媽媽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我來 她才能讓梨穗子更加幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的這麼想的話 就沒有必要再煩惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃早飯了哦 瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天西田先生有公事外出 今天就休息一天好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要出去買東西的話派車送你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了我在房間玩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就老老實實的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是瑪麗亞的媽媽 一定要瑪麗亞在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷貝個人資料是禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是做個筆記而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能給外人看的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張兩人幽會的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你老婆看看會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 已經沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天好像身體不太好的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待著別動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blade的版本也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陌生的面孔 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是次世代的NEO-GIN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女兒 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是瑪麗亞的媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道她的來歷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料中的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就是 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是瑪麗亞的姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這麼矮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是自然分娩的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料記錄她已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是舊的紀錄 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者 是故意篡改的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情隨便它好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去停車場在汽車裡等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一下 坐下來慢慢說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去買東西  能在這裡等一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 全部都是瑪麗亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是騙人的 都是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不可能會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  瑪麗亞在訓練還有學習都很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽是瑪麗亞的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不是和瑪麗亞在一起呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼多抱抱瑪麗亞呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 有著驚人的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 在這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像現在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是X-CON? 還是NEO-GIN?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 是在遠處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有著很強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 走回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打敗她的可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要多問 待在這裡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我會回來接你的
