Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種沒有根據的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是那麼回事 遺傳基因信息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那邊 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓她消失 讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽討厭瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我的媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也給我…消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了 受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澤為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺到了 梨穗子有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有媽媽的資格哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 不要躲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓我打中 瑪麗亞要生氣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 真讓人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有很香味道 但是去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澤 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也許不知道 但是這種怪物是存在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你們碰那孩子一根手指!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 已經不行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接下來得讓那個消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂用自己的力量是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不弄清楚的話沒有任何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡 立刻回收
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒這個必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你的媽媽正趕過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打敗那些怪物 是你媽媽的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是媽媽不回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為媽媽已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那個傢伙是為了誰在做這麼危險的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 全都是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙一直都只是為了你而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她最喜歡梨穗子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:18:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽!
