Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玲奈嗎 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的回收班已經在趕過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經 結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈 把那孩子交回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 研究已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我第一次在戰鬥中感受到了快感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為崩潰還是因為要保護那個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在研究著自己 結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻還是不能理解 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要理解
